== Time and location: ==

 * Thursday 24 June 2004, starting 18:00, ca 1 hr
 * Messegelände (exhibition zone, Ettlinger Str) -> Marktplatz (market) Karlsruhe, speeches (ca 15 min. walk, also on the way to [[http://www.karlsruhe.linux.de/Events/Linuxtag/fest.php|Kalug party]])

